 has technical challenges, including: (i) requirement for a more complex panel pixel design; (ii) disappointing scan-through of OLED panel despite it being thinner than LCD panel; and (iii) weakened scan-through performance due to overlayered panel module. As the new OLED iPhone won&rsquo;t support under-display fingerprint recognition, we now do not expect production ramp-up will be delayed again (we previously projected the ramp-up would be postponed to late October or later).&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.macrumors.com/2017/07/03/ming-chi-kuo-iphone-omit-touch-id/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macrumors.com%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2Fming-chi-kuo-iphone-omit-touch-id%2F&d=rnN3sZUNEYpahFPz0GwFH4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9a86360a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.macrumors.com/2017/07/03/ming-chi-kuo-iphone-omit-touch-id/</a></blockquote><br />\n End"},{"pid":"a1598fd85a556e74942e8b4c3279ca1ffc18fd95","tid":308491,"uid":42531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"唔係冇touch id吖成班on9，係個touch id唔會喺個mon上面吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bfaec80b054a38ac46d7e78cfe4fbe52aae958","tid":308491,"uid":42531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係冇touch id吖成班on9，係個touch id唔會喺個mon上面吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家d連登仔低質到，成班弱智學人上論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2f500bfe8f8022d56a49059716de97d4295eaf","tid":308491,"uid":76764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"留名睇炒車"},{"pid":"b083983645cea6c2d99c9857ebbae520fd1b9f87","tid":308491,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"iPhone8s 啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b3fe454a853669dc519a6